Subject: POC - Invalid object name 'dbo.SA_WebServer_Events'.
Description:
Nancy.RequestExecutionException: Oh noes! ---> System.Data.SqlClient.SqlException: Invalid object name 'dbo.SA_WebServer_Events'.

SQL Server authentication from NEA > SQL DB.
Opening Web Reports causing 500 error shown above.
Web Service was running as local system. Set to run as AD User wtih Rights to SQLServer/DB. 
Same error as above. 
 
NEA 11.6. Fresh install. ADI Tables present.
Solution_Comment__c:
Restarting the service had no impact on the problem. We saw the service go through a "restart" during the session but when reviewing the logs, no restarting of the service was recorded. Reboot failed to fix the problem so we went with reinstalling NEA as the next step. 

Web console is now running without issue post reinstall.
